## Pulley Problem.
## Part 1
## By F. Wolfs,  WOLFS@NSRL.ROCHESTER.EDU,
## No unauthorized commercial use
## Imported Files
## ${CAPA_Tools}Problem
## ${CAPA_GraphicsDirectory}Gtype20/prob08a.eps
